I had a wonderful experience at Chelsea Dental and am happy to have found a new dentist to call home!! After avoiding the dentist for 6-7 years, I was nervous to say the least! But the entire staff greeted me with warmth, and were friendly, concise and professional. Some reviews have said reception was ‚Äúrude‚Äù and I have to disagree‚Äîthey are SO efficient!
I actually laughed when I got off the phone with them and thought ‚Äúwhy can‚Äôt every appointment I make be that quick and easy??‚Äù
I was able to make a last minute appointment in less than 60 seconds on the phone as they squeezed me in, and I received an appointment reminder the day before. I found them to be extremely kind and efficient upon checking me in and out with paperwork etc.
The dental assistant was so welcoming and kind, and the dentist was so sweet, honest and genuinely empathetic. As I was leaving they suggested I do a cleaning same day to save me the hassle of having to book a second appointment for that, too! So thoughtful. I actually am looking forward to coming back in for my filling and toot canal ü§£I will tell all of my friends and clients to look no further than Chelsea Dental!

I've been afraid of the dentist my entire life. I almost ran away from the office  but something about Dr. Lalak just made me trust him and I must admit, this man was the best dentist I've ever seen in my 57 years.  So kind and patient with me.  My first ever PAIN FREE EXTRACTION  !!!! HONESTLY
I can't Thank Dr. Lalak enough with just 5 stars... Thank you
The entire staff is 5 star.

originalText.text: This was the first time I made an appt. here, after my regular dentist retired.  From the onset, the friendliness of the reception staff, to the assistant, Joseph, who did all my x-rays, put me at ease.  Then Dr. Halak, the dentist, did a thorough cleaning of my teeth WITHOUT me shedding any blood, which is customary for me during this procedure. The visit was fast and efficient; the office is clean and modern, and all of the equipment is high tech.  I highly recommend, not only this dentist, but also the entire practice.  Can't wait to go back in 6 months!
